@startuml
!theme plain
title 16. Roadmap Evidence Guardrails
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Source evidence" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Evidence classifier" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Claim matrix" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Report text" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Review gate" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : vendor/source data
N2 --> N3 : direct/adjacent/negative
N3 --> N4 : allowed wording
N4 --> N5 : publication claim

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
